<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5881148>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7A–7E. Nigripeza cali new species, Colombia, holotype male. A, head, dorsal; B, habitus, lateral; C, head, left lateral; D, terminalia, left lateral; E, abdomen, ventral. Abbreviations: bdp—basal distiphallus, c—cercus, e—epandrium, ea—ejaculatory apodeme, ed—ejaculatory duct, hy—hypandrium, pb—phallic bulb, ph—phallapodeme, pp—phallic plate, spp—sperm pump" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5881148/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5881160>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10A–10D. Nigripeza spangleri new species, Ecuador. A, spermatheca and associated structures; B, male sternite 5 and genital fork; C, male terminalia, lateral; D, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5881160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5881152>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8A–8F. Nigripeza obscura (Hennig).A, living male, Ecuador; B, male sternite 5 and genital fork; C, male terminalia, left lateral, with sperm pump and ejaculatory apodeme detached; D, spermatheca and associated structures; E, type female; F, living female, Ecuador." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5881152/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5881156>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9A–9F. Nigripeza octa new species, Costa Rica.A, head anterior; B, holotype male habitus; C, head lateral; D, male abdomen ventral; E, male terminalia, left lateral with aedeagal apodeme and sperm pump detached; F, living male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5881156/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

